        帶你快速掌握重點，</br>完整規範、評審標準、獎勵與注意事項請前往詳情頁查看。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col h-full relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none">
